metadata.name: The Last of Us - Desolation Road
metadata.description:
Spore covered cars slowly rusting away in trash covered streets. Behind the scenes, high quality image captured in Calgary, Alberta Canada on March 30, 2022. Own the original image before the series release. Titled Desolation Road as reverence to this soon to be hit series, "The Last of Us."

5595 x 3730 pixels
Canon EOS M50
f/2 1/25 sec. ISO 500
22 mm lens
